message.text:
𝘋𝘪𝘳𝘦𝘬 𝘮𝘰? 𝘋𝘪𝘳𝘦𝘬 𝘬𝘰? 𝘋𝘪𝘳𝘦𝘬 𝘯𝘢𝘵𝘪𝘯𝘨 𝘭𝘢𝘩𝘢𝘵!

𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐚 𝐩𝐢𝐧𝐤 𝐜𝐚𝐫𝐩𝐞𝐭 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐢𝐚𝐫𝐚, 𝐥𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐰𝐞𝐥𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐁𝐨𝐚𝐫𝐝 𝐨𝐟 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐬!💃 

The YWCA officers wouldn’t be complete without their lovely and gorgeous Directors for this school year! They embody the true essence of sYsterhood - beauty, brains, and kindness. 🩰

Secretariat Director: Alexie Tafalla
Public Relations Director: Alyssa Manuel
Liaison Director: Francheska Alvarez
Creatives Director: Denise Pepito

Special thanks to: Photo X Media

Caption by: Winona Caudilla
Pubmat by: Stefany Dela Cruz

#BoldHerFilipYna #HerStoricYWCA25

message.text:
𝘋𝘪𝘳𝘦𝘬 𝘮𝘰? 𝘋𝘪𝘳𝘦𝘬 𝘬𝘰? 𝘋𝘪𝘳𝘦𝘬 𝘯𝘢𝘵𝘪𝘯𝘨 𝘭𝘢𝘩𝘢𝘵!

𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐚 𝐩𝐢𝐧𝐤 𝐜𝐚𝐫𝐩𝐞𝐭 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐢𝐚𝐫𝐚, 𝐥𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐰𝐞𝐥𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐁𝐨𝐚𝐫𝐝 𝐨𝐟 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐬!💃 

The YWCA officers wouldn’t be complete without their lovely and gorgeous Directors for this school year! They embody the true essence of sYsterhood - beauty, brains, and kindness. 🩰

Secretariat Director: Alexie Tafalla
Public Relations Director: Alyssa Manuel
Liaison Director: Francheska Alvarez
Creatives Director: Denise Pepito

Special thanks to: Photo X Media

Caption by: Winona Caudilla
Pubmat by: Stefany Dela Cruz

message.text:
𝘋𝘪𝘳𝘦𝘬 𝘮𝘰? 𝘋𝘪𝘳𝘦𝘬 𝘬𝘰? 𝘋𝘪𝘳𝘦𝘬 𝘯𝘢𝘵𝘪𝘯𝘨 𝘭𝘢𝘩𝘢𝘵!

𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐚 𝐩𝐢𝐧𝐤 𝐜𝐚𝐫𝐩𝐞𝐭 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐢𝐚𝐫𝐚, 𝐥𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐰𝐞𝐥𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐁𝐨𝐚𝐫𝐝 𝐨𝐟 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐬!💃 

The YWCA officers wouldn’t be complete without their lovely and gorgeous Directors for this school year! They embody the true essence of sYsterhood - beauty, brains, and kindness. 🩰

Secretariat Director: Alexie Tafalla
Public Relations Director: Alyssa Manuel
Liaison Director: Francheska Alvarez
Creatives Director: Denise Pepito

Special thanks to: Photo X Media

Caption by: Winona Caudilla
Pubmat by: Stefany Dela Cruz

#BoldHerFilipYna #HerStoricYWCA25

message.text:
📢 ANNOUNCEMENT

The FEU Chorale auditions originally set for September 17 (Wednesday) will be postponed due to the scheduled transport strike. 🚧

We understand that many of you are eager to showcase your talent and join our growing family, but your safety and convenience come first. 💚🎶

A new audition schedule will be released soon, so please keep an eye on our official pages for further updates. Thank you for your patience and understanding—we can’t wait to hear your voices when the time comes! 🌟✨

#FEUChorale #FEU #Auditions #KanTamaraw

message.text:
📢 ANNOUNCEMENT

The FEU Chorale auditions originally set for September 17 (Wednesday) will be postponed due to the scheduled transport strike. 🚧

We understand that many of you are eager to showcase your talent and join our growing family, but your safety and convenience come first. 💚🎶

A new audition schedule will be released soon, so please keep an eye on our official pages for further updates. Thank you for your patience and understanding—we can’t wait to hear your voices when the time comes! 🌟✨

message.text:
📢 ANNOUNCEMENT

The FEU Chorale auditions originally set for September 17 (Wednesday) will be postponed due to the scheduled transport strike. 🚧

We understand that many of you are eager to showcase your talent and join our growing family, but your safety and convenience come first. 💚🎶

A new audition schedule will be released soon, so please keep an eye on our official pages for further updates. Thank you for your patience and understanding—we can’t wait to hear your voices when the time comes! 🌟✨

#FEUChorale #FEU #Auditions #KanTamaraw
